
To install Cocoapods, you'll need Ruby (ruby 2.3.7p456 is what I used).

Run 'sudo gem install cocoapods' from the project root.

Close Xcode

Run 'pod repo update'
Run 'pod install'

Open the .xcworkspace file NOT the .xcodeproj

More info here:
https://guides.cocoapods.org/using/getting-started.html
